<L>__{exterior factory. london. 1975. day}
<A>__{margaret is standing on an impromptu stage outside a factory. she has a hard hat on her head.}
<C>__{margaret}
<D>__{the trade union movement was founded to protect workers. now it persecutes them. it stops them from working. it is killing jobs and it is bringing this country to its knees. i say enough. it's time to get up. it's time to go to work. it's time to put the great back into great britain!}
